    <abstract id="aspace_8a08e2bacc575d20cefbffb0f99ea1fb">The William Ryder Mathers Collection of David Wojnarowicz and Montanna includes correspondence, collages and Twelve-Step program narratives written by Montanna Houston, an artist and writer who lived in New York City and later in Houston, Texas. The correspondence is mostly addressed to William Mathers, and there is one letter from Wojnarowicz to Montanna.</abstract>
